sentence: President  Biden  is  meeting  with  Israeli  Prime  Minister  Benjamin  Netanyahu  in  Tel  Aviv  on  Wednesday  as  the  White  House  shows  solidarity  with  its  chief  ally  in  the  Middle  East  after  Hamas  killed  some  1,400  Israelis  during  an  Oct.  7  attack.
